{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Pro|5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","chapter":5,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":1,"text":"My son, pay attention to my wisdom; listen closely to my understanding","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":2,"text":"so that you may maintain discretion and your lips safeguard knowledge.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":3,"text":"Though the lips of the forbidden woman drip honey and her words are smoother than oil,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":4,"text":"in the end she’s as bitter as wormwood and as sharp as a double-edged sword.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":5,"text":"Her feet go down to death; her steps head straight for Sheol.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":6,"text":"She doesn’t consider the path of life; she doesn’t know that her ways are unstable.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":7,"text":"So now, sons, listen to me, and don’t turn away from the words from my mouth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":8,"text":"Keep your way far from her. Don’t go near the door of her house.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":9,"text":"Otherwise, you will give up your vitality to others and your years to someone cruel;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":10,"text":"strangers will drain your resources, and your hard-earned pay will end up in a foreigner’s house.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":11,"text":"At the end of your life, you will lament when your physical body has been consumed,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":12,"text":"and you will say, “How I hated discipline, and how my heart despised correction.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":13,"text":"I didn’t obey my teachers or listen closely to my instructors.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":14,"text":"I am on the verge of complete ruin before the entire community.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":15,"text":"Drink water from your own cistern, water flowing from your own well.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":16,"text":"Should your springs flow in the streets, streams in the public squares?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":17,"text":"They should be for you alone and not for you to share with strangers.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":18,"text":"Let your fountain be blessed, and take pleasure in the wife of your youth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":19,"text":"A loving deer, a graceful doe — let her breasts always satisfy you; be lost in her love forever.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":20,"text":"Why, my son, would you lose yourself with a forbidden woman or embrace a wayward woman?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":21,"text":"For a man’s ways are before the Lord’s eyes, and he considers all his paths.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":22,"text":"A wicked man’s iniquities will trap him; he will become tangled in the ropes of his own sin.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:5:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Pro","bookOrder":19,"chapter":5,"verse":23,"text":"He will die because there is no discipline, and be lost because of his great stupidity.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5